    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD is a masterclass in lightweight engineering, powered by the iconic sequential twin-turbocharged 13B-REW rotary engine. The powerplant exhibits superb compression across all rotor faces, while the five-speed manual transmission provides crisp, positive engagement through every gate. The chassis remains true to its 50/50 weight distribution, featuring a factory-original Torsen limited-slip differential and untouched double-wishbone suspension. With its original paint and a cockpit free of bolster wear or UV damage, this collector-tier specimen offers a pure, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare to find in such an unmolested state.",
      "price": 48500.0,
